        <item>
            <title>【评测】Acer Nitro GA1 电竞荧幕，内置 Google TV + HDMI/USBC/DP 连接埠 + Mac 用家抵用荧幕之选</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/acer-nitro-ga1/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=acer-nitro-ga1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/acer-nitro-ga1/wireless-home/desktop-pc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 12:29:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Notebook 配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291180</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Acer 早前推出的 Acer Nitro GA1 电竞智能显示器到了香港，这款显示器特色在于内置 Google TV 作业系统，而且更同时备有 HDMI, DisplayPort 还有 USB-C 视讯支援，可说是满足用家 3 个愿望&#8211;直接连接 Mac 电脑作为屏幕、为手提电脑充电，而且也可连接 PS5、Xbox 等游戏机，也可驳桌面电脑，直连高阶显示卡的 DisplayPort 插口。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04869-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04869-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04869.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291197" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04848-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04848-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04848.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04806-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04806-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04806.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Acer Nitro GA1 是一款专为游戏玩家设计的显示器，提供 27 吋，与 31.5 吋，两种尺寸选择，今次我们就测试 27 吋型号。萤幕解析度为 2560 × 1440（1440p），并具备 180Hz 更新率，为游戏提供流畅的画面显示体验。在连接 PS5 之后，我们可启动 120Hz 选项，在连接 PS5 Pro 之后，测试玩游戏《Marvel Spider-Man 2》享受超高流畅度，在城市中自由跳跃比很多电视机还要爽快。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291196" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04851-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04851-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04851.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一条 USB-C 线就可将 Mac 电脑影像输出到这部荧幕，另荧幕内置有喇叭，可播放电脑声音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04854-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04854-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04854.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04799-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04799-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04799.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲荧幕内置的多款模式，可迎合电脑、游戏、影片播放的需要，提供更强色彩表现或 HDR 表现</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04800-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04800-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04800.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲荧幕提供 AMD FreeSync 支援，在玩游戏时大幅减低画面「撕裂」现象</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291198" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04849-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04849-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04849.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04801-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04801-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04801.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 PS5 的 120Hz 输出</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291194" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04861-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04861-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04861.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在游玩《Marvel&#8217;s Spider-Man 2》等支援 120Hz 模式的游戏时，可获得更为畅快的游戏体验，当然驳 PS5 Pro 就更好</p><p>外观设计方面，Nitro GA1 采用具备电竞风格的支架设计，符合 Nitro 系列的美学，支援高度调整及旋转成直立模式（Portrait Mode），适合不同的使用需求。全身白色的设计，与 PS5 等白色设计的硬件十分合衬。连接埠部分，该显示器配备 HDMI、DisplayPort 及 USB-C，确保多样化的连接选项，提升兼容性。USB-C 连接可驳 Mac mini、MacBook 等苹果电脑，直接显示画面，并为手提电脑充电。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04784-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04784-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04784.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲操作都在机背，而且十分简单，只有一个开关按钮与 joystick</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04781-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04781-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04781.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲内置用家都需要的 HDMI, DisplayPort, USB-C 插口，更有 2 个 USB-A 插口给你连接滑鼠电脑</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04783-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04783-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04783.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04786-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04786-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04786.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04805-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04805-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04805.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲荧幕设计超幼边，配合全白色机身，与 PS5 游戏机等白色硬件十分合衬</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04797-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04797-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04797.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲你可同时连接桌面电脑、PS5 等游戏机、Mac 电脑，在选单内自由切换</p><p>Acer Nitro GA1 本身是一个智能荧幕，它内置有 Google TV 系统。在登入 Google 帐户后，你可在电视安装任何 Google TV 兼容 App，系统本身就安装了 Apple TV、Amazon Prime Video、Netflix、Disney+ 等，这些都可在毋须开电脑、游戏机的情况下，直接利用本智能荧幕的遥控，操作睇戏、睇片。比起其他智能电视系统，Google TV 用家可自由安装 VPN 等应用程式，应用范畴更加广泛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291200" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04790-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04790-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04790.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能荧幕附随遥控器，毋须开电脑都可播放串流影片、睇 YouTube</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04796-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04796-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04796.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04795-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04795-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04795.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Google TV 好处是让你随意安装 Google TV 兼容应用程式（更可安装部份 Android 应用程式），例如 VPN 等，应用范畴更广</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04847-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04847-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04847.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要特别提的是荧幕本身已有防反光设计，即使如图找两盏大光灯照住，反光的程度也是非常低</p><h2>结语：价值在于多种类连接</h2><p>在电脑商场逛一下你会发现千多元都有好多 27 吋荧幕选择，之不过今次介绍的 Acer Nitro GA1（GA271U）胜在有多种输入，把桌面电脑、手提电脑、游戏机同一时间连接入这个荧幕都无问题。而且它更内置 Google TV 智能系统，即使不用开电脑，也可在荧幕上收看 Apple TV, Netflix, Disney+ 等串流影视 App，甚至其他 Android App（受到一定限制，并非所有 App 都能安装／使用），例如我们常用的 VPN，都可在这个平台使用（当然常见的 Surfshark, NordVPN 等其实都有 Google TV 版）。在打机来说，这部荧幕输出色彩较为鲜艳，具备有各种游戏、HDR 模式，亦具有 180Hz 更新率适合中阶打机用家。如果你认为 2K 荧幕都够用的话，Acer Nitro GA1 系列可在你的考虑之列。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/acer-nitro-ga1/wireless-home/desktop-pc/">【评测】Acer Nitro GA1 电竞荧幕，内置 Google TV + HDMI/USBC/DP 连接埠 + Mac 用家抵用荧幕之选</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
