        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本「ZZZN 睡眠服装系统」亮相，隔音降噪 + 智能戒指监测睡眠质素</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/zzzn-sleep-system/life-tech/health/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zzzn-sleep-system</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/zzzn-sleep-system/life-tech/health/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:43:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ZZZN SLEEP APPAREL SYSTEM]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[睡眠]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291081</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>有调查显示，日本人的睡眠时间严重不足。有见及此，日本科研公司 NTT DX Partners 联同 Konel 株式会社及物联网研发企业 SOXAI，近期携手推出 「ZZZN SLEEP APPAREL SYSTEM（ZZZN 睡眠服装系统）」，盼能为受失眠困扰人士提供快速入睡解决方法，提升使用者睡眠体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/25_01080087ssize-694x520.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/25_01080087ssize-694x520.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/25_01080087ssize.jpeg 1201w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://apparel.zzzn.jp/">apparel.zzzn.jp</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291095" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/zzzn_fv_retina-424x580.jpeg" alt="" width="424" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/zzzn_fv_retina-424x580.jpeg 424w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/zzzn_fv_retina.jpeg 658w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 424px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://apparel.zzzn.jp/">apparel.zzzn.jp</a></p><p>ZZZN 睡眠服装系统由羽绒服、头饰及智能睡眠监测戒指三部分组成。羽绒服设计灵感源自日本传统御寒衣物 「夜着」，经现代化改良，使其更贴合当代人的睡眠需求。用户可透过调节袖子与下摆的拉绳及袖口束带，自由调整至最舒适状态。内部填充物采用「光电子纤维」，轻盈保暖，并透过使用者体温维持衣物内部温度，确保持续温暖，营造良好的睡眠环境。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1964-387x580.jpeg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1964-387x580.jpeg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1964.jpeg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头饰可分拆，图片来源：<a href="https://apparel.zzzn.jp/">apparel.zzzn.jp</a></p><p>ZZZN 睡眠服装系统设有充气式帽子，可为头部提供稳定支撑，让使用者无论身处家中、办公室，甚至旅途中，都能轻松进入放松状态。帽内亦配备耳机与光线调节功能，具备卓越的隔音效果，还能播放两种助眠频率的音乐，帮助用户更快入眠。灯光系统则会根据使用者状态调整，例如模拟日落般的红光，以营造自然睡意；而在清晨，则结合音乐与蓝光，以柔和方式唤醒使用者，确保清醒过程不至于过于突兀。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291094" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1838-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1838-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1838.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh0927-387x580.jpeg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh0927-387x580.jpeg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh0927.jpeg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设计概念盼使用者身处任何地方均可进入放松状态，图片来源：<a href="https://apparel.zzzn.jp/">apparel.zzzn.jp</a></p><p>智能戒指可即时监测心率、体温及压力指数，协助用户深入分析自身的睡眠品质及各阶段变化，提升健康管理效率，达至更全面的个人化睡眠调节方案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/productimg17118ea90-436x580.jpg" alt="" width="436" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/productimg17118ea90-436x580.jpg 436w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/productimg17118ea90.jpg 676w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 436px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需配合智能戒指使用，图片来源：<a href="https://apparel.zzzn.jp/">apparel.zzzn.jp</a></p><p>这款融合尖端科技与时尚设计的 「ZZZN 睡眠服装系统」，预计将于 2025 年大阪关西世界博览会展出，能否掀起市场热潮，成为未来智能睡眠产品的典范，值得拭目以待。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1708-387x580.jpeg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1708-387x580.jpeg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1708.jpeg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1999-387x580.jpeg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1999-387x580.jpeg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsh1999.jpeg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://apparel.zzzn.jp/">apparel.zzzn.jp</a>、 <a href="https://www.technice.com.tw/experience/enterprise/163808/">Tech Nice</a>、<a href="https://www.designboom.com/technology/zzzn-coat-sleeping-bag-headpiece-red-light-doze-off-anywhere-apparel-system-02-10-2025/">Designs Boom</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/zzzn-sleep-system/life-tech/health/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
