            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291055</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日 LG 邀请了小编出席 2025 年第一季度产品巡礼，席间展示了全球首款透明 OLED 电视 LG SIGNATURE OLED T，LG 第二代 Styler 、PuriCare AeroBooster 和 PuriCare AeroFurniture 夜幕黑版本，实在令人目不暇接。现在就让小编和大家一起看看这些新家电！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04823-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04823-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04823.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04826-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04826-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04826.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04828-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04828-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04828.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 无界视觉体验</h2><p>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 是 LG 今年首季度创新重点产品。LG SIGNATURE OLED T 是全球首款 77 吋透明 OLED 电视，采用真正 4K 无线显示技术，突破现有电视技术框架，重新定义家居娱乐体验。用户可在「透明」与「非透明」显示模式间自由切换，确保电视既能播放影像，也能融入空间设计，提升视觉美感。</p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="LG Signature OLED T，全球首款透明 OLED 电视机" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1055456027?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>▲由「非透明模式」转换至「透明模式」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/17fff3b35bdb459e9bf0-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/17fff3b35bdb459e9bf0-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/17fff3b35bdb459e9bf0.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设定为透明显示模式时，可以看穿电视背面</p><div></div><div></div><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0bde5c47-4e06-42c5-8f04-14ce0aa47ee1" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1055461878?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>▲非透明显示模式</p><p>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 电视通过 Zero Connect Box 无线传输技术运作，摆脱传统有线连接的束缚，减少杂乱线材影响空间整洁感。此款创新的电视采用 LG α11 AI 处理器，能够提供卓越色彩、对比度，并提升音效表现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04838-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04838-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04838-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在关掉电视后，开启 BAR MODE 画面下方显示天气、财经、体育资讯，而电视上方保持透明</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04837-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04837-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04837.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲放大资讯</p><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04833-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04833-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04833.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04834-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04834-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04834.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲可设定关闭电视时显示名画或用户指定的图片，令空间变得更有艺术感</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="8b1c21be-7075-461e-8b35-d143f937403a" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1055458370?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04807-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04807-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04807.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲电视背面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04814-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04814-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04814.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲电视背面微距观看</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04816-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04816-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04816.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲无线盒子，以无线方式传输讯号到电视</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291065" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8bd931cf54964ebb9a49-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8bd931cf54964ebb9a49-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8bd931cf54964ebb9a49.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1aa5b4c8e9343079438-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1aa5b4c8e9343079438-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1aa5b4c8e9343079438.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1165edb38c449bf9d1d-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1165edb38c449bf9d1d-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1165edb38c449bf9d1d.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 可以设定为 T-Object 模式（常开显示功能）以将荧幕设定为数码画布，另外亦设有 T-Bar 优雅讯息列，能够增加空间气氛，让 LG SIGNATURE OLED T 可融入日常生活场景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lgsignatureoledt2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lgsignatureoledt2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lgsignatureoledt2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2dd23ce8878a4b788f48-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2dd23ce8878a4b788f48-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2dd23ce8878a4b788f48.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/69061e3c997944579e1f-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/69061e3c997944579e1f-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/69061e3c997944579e1f.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><h2>LG 第二代 Styler 新增高压蒸气挂熨机</h2><p>LG 第二代 Styler 采用升级版高压蒸气技术，结合作双重蒸气衣物护理技术及 AI 智能侦测技术，可根据衣物重量、长度自动推荐最佳护理模式。</p><p>LG 第二代 Styler 透过天然蒸汽 99.9% 抗菌功能去除异味与细菌。可于 20 分钟，内完成衣物整理。此外第二代 Styler 设有「智慧摇摆衣架」，透过 6 大摆动技术（抖动、摆动、甩动、飘动、摇动、整平）模拟拍打与摆动动作，更容易去除灰尘与折痕，提升护理效果。Styler 内置高压蒸气挂熨机，具有 3 段式高压蒸气，能够迅速抚平衣服皱折。确保日常使用更便捷。适合繁忙都市人或对高端服饰有精致护理需求的用户。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9c830c1456dd49c29336-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9c830c1456dd49c29336-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9c830c1456dd49c29336.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><br /><b>
